snippet.title: Miniland - Trailer | STEAM
snippet.description:
Miniland is a game where you can do anything you want to! 😍 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1934040/Miniland/
Steam wishlist now to get updated! ✅

Build your dream house, by exploring, collecting resources, crafting, building, fighting and farming!  Start with a small patch of land, that with time you can expand by yourself with biome tiles that you receive every day. 🔥

#miniland #gameplaytrailer #pixelart
